"{\n  \"text\": \"I grew too much parsley. It just went nuts on me. So I cut it back. And I cut it back quite a bit. I was thinking I'd make some chimichuri. Uh, what else would you do with this much parsley? I mean that's a lot of parsley. So I chopped it all up and put it in my food processor, and I added some salt and some dried oregano and some chili pepper, a half a cup of red white vinegar, some olive oil, grinded it all up, scraped some off the side just to make sure it was all evenly done, finished grinding it up. Put it into my already full container of a lifetime supply of chimichuri. And now I uh tonight I made a steak to try it out. And it was the best thing I'd ever had in my whole life. Fresh chimichuri is just wonderful. This is the beauty of having an herb garden. This is why you do it. Oh, it was so dang good. And you know, I was saying a lifetime supply of chimichuri, make that three meals. Oh, it's gonna be gone.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" I grew too much parsley.\",\n      \"start\": 0.32,\n      \"end\": 1.84,\n      \"duration\": 1.52,\n      \"confidence\": 0.985,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" I\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" gre\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.97\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"w\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" to\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"o\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\